## Improvement: Duplicate books can be created (same title, author, ISBN)


### Description
 allows duplicate books with identical `title`, `author`, and `isbn`.

### Steps to reproduce
1. POST a book with title/author/isbn A
2. POST the same details again
3. Two separate records are created

#### Example curl
```bash
{

}
```

### Expected
- First request: 201 Created
- Second request: 409 Conflict (or 400) with message: "Book already exists"
- Only one record stored for the same ISBN

### Actual
- Both requests return 201 Created, two records created
http://localhost:3000/book/34
http://localhost:3000/book/35

### Suggested fix
- Add uniqueness check 

