## Improvement: Title input has no character limit (UI)

### Description
"Add Book" form does not enforce a character limit for Title, which allows extremely long strings that break layout.

### Steps to reproduce
1. Open Add Book form (http://localhost:3000/add-book)
2. Enter a very long title (500+ chars) example : 'No Matter How Much You Promise to Cook or Pay the Rent You Blew It Cauze Bill Bailey Ain't Never Coming Home Again'
3. Submit and observe UI/layout issues
This might cuase web to crash as buffer issue 

### Suggested fix
- Add maxLength={200}
---

## Improvement: Author input has no character limit (UI)


### Description
Author field allows very long strings (300+ chars), causing UI issues.

### Steps to reproduce
1. Open Add Book form
2. Enter a very long Author (500+ chars) example : 'No Matter How Much You Promise to Cook or Pay the Rent You Blew It Cauze Bill Bailey Ain't Never Coming Home Again'
3. Submit and observe behavior

This might cuase web to crash as buffer issue 
### Suggested fix
- Add maxLength={100}


